    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>组建一支活化物品组成的超强小队，在这款史诗级卡牌战斗游戏中碾压你的对手。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了摆脱无聊的日常，当地一家大型超市的员工们决定在午休时间自创一款稀奇古怪却令人上瘾的卡牌游戏。这个小游戏原本仅供消遣，却很快演变成席卷整个超市的热潮。你是刚入职的新人，渴望证明自己，并在对决中一路晋升，跻身于<i>《午休战术》</i>的排行榜之上。你的心里怀着一个目标：成为<span class=\"bb_strike\">本月最佳员工</span>终极卡牌大师！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002240/extras/91c3f1f3f62b90c5cb7546cf5f0251ff.poster.avif?t=1771951777\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002240/extras/91c3f1f3f62b90c5cb7546cf5f0251ff.webm?t=1771951777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >定义你的玩法风格</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《午休战术》的每一局游戏开始时，你都要做出三个简单却至关重要的选择：一个英雄和两个阵营。你的英雄会赋予你一个特殊的被动技能，而两个阵营则决定了你在游戏中能获得的单位类型。接下来，组建一支小队，在十三回合的对战中击败对手，赢得声望并在排行榜上不断晋升！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无尽的组合搭配</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从上百个单位与数十位英雄中自由组合搭配，创造完美的协同联动效果。这里有无限可能！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002240/extras/d9d7b12e6ae497a074e5f761ca5eddc2.poster.avif?t=1771951777\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002240/extras/d9d7b12e6ae497a074e5f761ca5eddc2.webm?t=1771951777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >找到自己的节奏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用异步多人设计，这意味着你可以完全按照自己的节奏来玩——随时随地，快慢皆宜。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可爱又搞怪的角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日常物品被赋予生命，纷纷化身为法师与女巫、圣骑士与海盗等角色闪亮登场。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >午休时的完美游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上手简单轻松，却乐趣无穷，这无疑是你可以在之后的午休时间里用于打发时间的完美游戏——还有更多精彩内容敬请期待！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002240/extras/3e074be9134846d991a3830a589f7736.poster.avif?t=1771951777\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002240/extras/3e074be9134846d991a3830a589f7736.webm?t=1771951777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
